{"tid":1467872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推咁多垃圾post 不如早啲傾個共識出嚟仲好啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:12.000Z","uid":209617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fdcc4bbc420a8dd34416a79abb958cf1bd71f87","tid":1467872,"uid":209617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:34.000Z","msg":"1. 究竟係隔日塞 定係日日都要塞?<br />\n<br />\n2. 大家同唔同意少人就宣傳，一到放工時間手足開始入機場，等多人就自然塞到呢樣野? (當然其他人唔好等到放工時間先去啦，要出就盡早出)<br />\n<br />\n3. 機場始終都係和理非主場，手足們唔會主動勇武，但如果係自衛而勇武就點都唔割，呢點同唔同意?<br />\n<br />\n4. 係手足嘅都知唔可以搞FA同記者，如果有人咁做就係鬼，呢點同唔同意?<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果搞清楚真係鬼，唔會對佢主動出手，最多圍佢綁起唔比佢走，呢點同唔同意?因為始終都係和理非<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權，五大訴求，缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"76d18a316558573983594c8f8ad3a112fd87d99e","tid":1467872,"uid":209617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b3ae27e36c5a4391f12a228d943defe3635e2a","tid":1467872,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"900b49974117b6fbd35f15669bc32dad3a9b696a","tid":1467872,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n到而家都唔知聽日到底有無人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386e2b20a3019c1f19632a05e6608dddd75d79cf","tid":1467872,"uid":209617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d77826d792b6d82b2592a28aa9c9627b4a8331c","tid":1467872,"uid":209617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:44.0